\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}^{+}\geq\frac{3}{4}\overline{R}$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

,
 we have 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}^{-}\geq0$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

.
