\begin_inset Formula $x^{-}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $s^{-}$
\end_inset

 are positive.
 Finally,
 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{\theta}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $s^{\theta}$
\end_inset

 are positive.
 This proves that 
\begin_inset Formula $(\frac{t}{c+t/\overline{R}},\frac{t}{c+t/\overline{R}}-x_{\circ},\overline{R})$
\end_inset

